action.title: Action
action.description: The fists are furious, the guns are blazing, and the drama is sizzling in these edge-of-your-seat hits.

283943.title: Hunt to Kill
283943.description: A border patrol agent quits and moves to the woods with his daughter, but when she is kidnapped by a band of criminals he steps back into action.

289779.title: 5th Street
289779.description: A husband in inner-city Los Angeles is determined to track down the gang responsible for murdering his wife in this gritty action thriller.

302149.title: Code Of Silence
302149.description: A karate cop takes on a corrupt department and two feuding crime families. He has the chops to do it.

302326.title: Gang Related
302326.description: Two men face the consequences after they kill a man and pin the murder on an innocent transient.

302505.title: The Substitute
302505.description: Undercover as a substitute teacher, an ex-marine cleans up the crime-infested school when he discovers a gang tormenting students and staff.

304799.title: The Bounty
304799.description: An idyllic voyage to Tahiti in 1789 turns a crew aboard the H.M.S. Bounty against its captain when they find tropical paradise and unlimited sex.

305801.title: The Bridge at Remagen
305801.description: As the Allied Forces advance towards the last bridge on the Rhine, German forces must assess the real human cost of their war strategy.

305818.title: Harley Davidson And The Marlboro Man
305818.description: Two modern-day "Robin Hoods" heist an armored car full of drugs, putting them in the sights of hired killers and on a ride for their lives.

306929.title: The Devil's Brigade
306929.description: In this true WWII story, an American colonel creates the First Special Service Force from a group of misfits. A dangerous mission soon awaits.

306944.title: Remo Williams: The Adventure Begins...
306944.description: A cop, recruited by a secret agency out to avenge society's wrongs, cuts him loose on the bad guys of the world.

306946.title: Run Silent, Run Deep
306946.description: With sweat-dripping realism, this taut drama stars Clark Gable as a single-minded sub commander who must contend with a tough executive officer (Burt Lancaster) and attacks from enemy forces.

307753.title: Kickboxer
307753.description: After a kickboxing champ is paralyzed fighting Thailand’s top fighter, his brother vows vengeance but must learn Muay Thai to fight back.

316456.title: The Spy Next Door
316456.description: A man asked to baby-sit his neighbor's children winds up having to fight off secret agents after one of the kids inadvertently downloads a secret code.

334156.title: Mad Max
334156.description: A vengeful cop and a sadistic motorcycle gang face off in a chaotic wasteland.

348456.title: The Good, the Bad and the Ugly
348456.description: Clint Eastwood portrays the invincible "Man With No Name" in a lethal pursuit of $200,000 in Confederate money.  Lee Van Cleef and Eli Wallach also star in this renowned western.

348932.title: Escape Plan
348932.description: An incarcerated structural engineer teams up with another inmate to break out of a top-secret, high-security prison in this non-stop action-thriller.

367626.title: 2012: Doomsday
367626.description: As the date of the apocalypse nears, several strangers travel to a temple in Mexico to prevent an ancient prophecy from destroying the world.

367706.title: Jailbait
367706.description: She killed her stepfather in self-defense. Now, Anna must fight her dark side and survive the world of girl gangs and predatory guards in juvy.

367819.title: Titanic 2
367819.description: A century after the fateful voyage of the original, modern luxury liner Titanic II sets sail. Will this ship suffer the same fate as her namesake?

375599.title: The Magnificent Seven
375599.description: Yul Brynner stars as one of seven master gunmen pitted against an army of marauding bandits in this rousing action tale that launched the film careers of Steve McQueen, Charles Bronson and James Coburn.

382248.title: Asteroid: Final Impact
382248.description: Nobody believes a disgraced whistleblower scientist who detects a giant asteroid barreling toward Earth leaving him alone to save the planet.

389503.title: Robocop
389503.description: A cop who died in the line of duty is transformed into a chrome-plated cyborg policeman with an indestructible new body and a thirst for revenge.

417720.title: Tekken
417720.description: In 2039, when territories are run by corporations, a warrior rises from the streets to avenge his mother's death by entering a fighting competition.

448434.title: Bait
448434.description: When a freak tsunami traps people inside a supermarket, a pack of killer sharks let them know they aren’t the only ones who are shopping for dinner.

456931.title: Nine Lives
456931.description: A case of mistaken identity thrusts a former Special Forces agent suffering from PTSD back into the world of treachery he has tried to leave behind.

460057.title: Marauders
460057.description: An untraceable group of elite bank robbers is chased by an FBI agent who uncovers a deeper conspiracy behind the robbery-homicides.

461204.title: The Forbidden Kingdom
461204.description: A mystical staff transports an American teen to China, where he joins a band of martial-arts warriors to free the imprisoned Monkey King.

463206.title: El Pistolero
463206.description: Un poderoso llega a un pueblo en busca de nuevos pistoleros para su equipo y un hombre sencillo acepta el trabajo para vengar la muerte de su padre.

465295.title: Guardians (English Dub)
465295.description: Formed during the Cold War, an elite squad of superheroes return to action when new threats arise that threaten the safety of the world.

466386.title: Daylight's End
466386.description: In a future teeming with blood-hungry creatures, a rogue drifter reluctantly agrees to help a band of survivors find their way to a safe haven.

467930.title: Arn: The Knight Templar
467930.description: As punishment for a forbidden love, a brave Swedish nobleman is sent on a treacherous journey to the Holy Land as a Knight Templar.

472710.title: Lionheart
472710.description: After the murder of his brother, a tough soldier goes AWOL and enters the underground world of bare-knuckle fighting to support his family.

476644.title: The Boondock Saints
476644.description: Irish brothers try to clean up Boston’s underworld by knocking off gangsters and become local folk heroes, as an FBI agent traces their bloody trail.

477962.title: Set It Off
477962.description: Four African-American women in Los Angeles, all in dire financial circumstances, resort to robbing banks with action-packed, tragic consequences.

486566.title: Over the Top
486566.description: A truck driver attempts to reconnect with his estranged son as he road trips to Las Vegas to compete in an arm wrestling championship.

490029.title: After Effect
490029.description: Six college students signs up for a paid research study, not realizing they are subjects of a government experiment that will turn them into zombies.

494842.title: Shottas
494842.description: Two young men from Jamaica climb to the top of the criminal world in Miami, with a constant presence of drugs, extortion, and deceit.

497642.title: Fist of Fury
497642.description: Bruce Lee stars in this iconic action film about a student who fights for the honor of the oppressed Chinese people and to avenge his master’s murder

507852.title: Above the Shadows
507852.description: A woman who became literally invisible to others after her mother died works as a sleuth until meeting a jaded fighter, the only one who can see her.

512448.title: New Jack City
512448.description: Two streetwise cops embark on the riskiest mission of their careers when they go undercover to bust a ruthless drug kingpin reigning over Harlem.

520213.title: Train to Busan (Dubbed)
520213.description: A father and his estranged daughter are trapped on a speeding train full of fellow passengers when a zombie virus breaks out in South Korea.

521967.title: Absolute Deception
521967.description: After her FBI informant husband is murdered, a journalist teams up with a federal agent in Australia’s wealthy Gold Coast to solve the crime.

522586.title: A Man Apart
522586.description: A DEA agent, hell-bent on vengeance after a new drug kingpin murders his wife, enlists the former cartel boss in his lawless quest for justice.

527970.title: Blitz
527970.description: A tough cop and his sidekick, who faces ridicule from their homophobic squad, are dispatched to take down a serial killer who targets the police.

534020.title: Standoff
534020.description: Suspenseful drama about a psychotic assassin who breaks into the house of a man guarding a 12-year-old girl who witnessed a murder in broad daylight.

543161.title: Apocalypto
543161.description: A Mayan warrior braves the treacherous jungle to fight off attacking members of an opposing tribe in order to save his family.

543987.title: Parker
543987.description: Based on the Donald E. Westlake novels, a thief works by a code of integrity and makes it his mission to avenge all that cross him or work dirty.

545226.title: The Siege of Firebase Gloria
545226.description: After a hellish trek through enemy territory, a sergeant and his unit fight for their lives inside a base under siege by the Viet Cong.

552216.title: Get the Gringo
552216.description: When a career criminal is nabbed by Mexican authorities and placed in a tough prison, he must  learn to survive, with the help of a young boy.

554502.title: Brooklyn's Finest
554502.description: Throughout one week, the lives of three very different New York City police officers change as a result of a violent drug operation.

555463.title: La Suburban Dorada
555463.description: Por ayudar a su primo, un judicial es acusado de estar coludido con el narco y, para recuperar a su hijo, tiene que involucrarse con ellos.

555469.title: Calles Sin Nombre
555469.description: Un campeón de lucha libre trata de encausar a su sobrino por el buen camino para que no quede atrapado en la vida callejera de las drogas y el crimen.

557519.title: After Earth
557519.description: Following a crash landing on Earth, a young boy and his estranged father must make an arduous journey and survive the elements to signal for help.

559448.title: En El Infierno (Doblado)
559448.description: Dentro de la prisión más corrupta de Europa del Este, un prisionero cumpliendo cadena perpetua se enfrenta a un alcaide en una lucha a muerte.

559459.title: Blitz (Español)
559459.description: Un policía fuerte es designado para atrapar a un asesino en serie que ataca a oficiales de policía.

561851.title: 2Eleven
561851.description: Two brothers and fellow hustlers with very different motivations for committing robberies come to blows the more their criminal enterprise grows.

561888.title: Five-O
561888.description: The story of two Detroit police officers who get in over their heads when they decide to take a crooked path involving a ruthless drug lord.

562786.title: Patriot: A Nation at War
562786.description: A disavowed CIA agent goes on the run when mercenaries learned she possesses a memory card that could start World War III.

565416.title: Damage
565416.description: Ex-con John Brickner joins an underground fighting community to pay for the heart transplant of the daughter of the man he killed.

569769.title: Pandorum
569769.description: Panic and terror come fast as two astronauts wake up in an empty spacecraft with no memory of what happened - except that an evil entity is waiting.

572750.title: The Blackout: Invasion Earth
572750.description: A military crew discovers an outpost of survivors surrounded by corpses, from cars to hospitals, and tries to find out the cause of the mass deaths.

580532.title: Lucky Number Slevin
580532.description: A mysterious man is roped into a dangerous feud between two rival crime kingpins, neither of whom can step foot outside for fear of assassination.

581594.title: All About the Benjamins
581594.description: A bounty hunter’s botched capture of an inmate gets them stalked by diamond thieves who know one of them has a $60-million-winning lottery ticket.

589163.title: Hannibal Rising
589163.description: As in the Thomas Harris novel, the orphaned young Hannibal Lecter begins plotting bloody revenge, after his baby sister is killed during World War II.

589292.title: The Mask
589292.description: Jim Carrey’s superstar role as a kind and meek bank teller who gets super powers from a Nordic mask and becomes a totally s-s-s-smokin’ hero!

589323.title: Superhero Movie
589323.description: In this hilarious parody of beloved blockbusters, a nerdy teenager is bitten by a radioactive dragonfly, which gives him superhuman abilities.

590109.title: Casablanca Express
590109.description: During WW II, tension and swift action is triggered when the Allies find out that Nazi commandos are planning to hijack Winston Churchill’s train.

593782.title: Deep Blue Sea
593782.description: A scientist using genetically altered shark tissue to regenerate human brains fights for her life when the huge sharks breach her deep-sea station.

601995.title: The Alliance
601995.description: It’s been twenty years since four drug dealers have formed a peaceful pact, but after one member takes revenge on another, all hell breaks loose.

602253.title: Jupiter Ascending
602253.description: The visionaries of ‘The Matrix’ films return with the thrilling story of a genetically engineered tracker who informs a woman of her cosmic destiny.

602257.title: The Second Coming of Christ
602257.description: During The Rapture, a woman scientist comes to the end of her journey at the end of times and discovers that true faith can produce miracles.

608219.title: Gone in 60 Seconds
608219.description: To save his kid brother’s life from the mob, legendary retired car thief Memphis Raines will have to steal 50 cars and he has just one night to do it.

609489.title: The Humanity Bureau
609489.description: Nicolas Cage stars as a case agent in the year 2030 out to save a mother and son in the climate ravaged Midwest whom the government has exiled.

609505.description: Five strangers start their day living their lives and end up banding together in an elevator in the World Trade Center on 9//11 before it collapses.

610966.title: The League of Extraordinary Gentlemen
610966.description: A team of fantastical superheroes from literary tales are assembled by a notorious adventurer in order to save the planet from annihilation.

613784.title: Hercules Y La Conquista De La Atlantida
613784.description: La reina de la Atlántida conspira para apoderarse del mundo y, cuando el rey de Tebas es secuestrado, su fiel compañero Hércules sale al rescate.

617476.title: The Guardian
617476.description: A jaded Coast Guard trainer butts heads with an arrogant young recruit, as the two prepare for deadly missions and daunting rescues.

619654.title: Ip Man (English Dub)
619654.description: Tells the story of the brutality of the 1939 Japanese occupation of China through the eyes of the Wing Chun grandmaster who rose to fight against it.

619656.title: Ip Man 2 (English Dub)
619656.description: When the Wing Chun grandmaster moves to Hong Kong to open a school for the next generation of fighters, he’s forced to take on a corrupt cabal.

620779.title: Siberia
620779.description: After an American diamond merchant and his lover fall into a bad business deal in Russia, they must evade crossfire between the buyer and Feds.

620882.title: Rogue
620882.description: After an American travel journalist heads to the Australian outback to view ancient landmarks, he encounters a man-eating crocodile.

620940.title: Cartels
620940.description: A team of top DEA agents is assigned to protect a ruthless drug lord awaiting his execution, until an explosive ambush traps them.

621292.title: Black Dog
621292.description: An ex-convict truck driver with makes one last no-questions-asked trip, only to discover that his rig is stocked with assault weapons.

625413.title: The Scorpion King: Book of Souls
625413.description: When an evil warlord gains a sword that can steal souls, the Scorpion King and the sister of a Nubian king must find the one thing that can stop him.

625417.title: The Scorpion King 2: Rise of a Warrior
625417.description: After an evil general murders his father, the Scorpion King descends into the underworld to face a fearsome foe and reclaim the Sword of Damocles.

625420.title: The Scorpion King 3: Battle for Redemption
625420.description: When the Scorpion King is hired to guard a beleaguered king, things are not as they seem, so it is up to him and a lady assassin to save Scandinavia.

626763.title: Above Suspicion
626763.description: “Game of Thrones” star Emilia Clarke leads this true crime thriller as an informant whose help with an FBI agent leads to a deadly aftermath.

628238.title: Accident Man
628238.description: A seasoned hitman whose calling card is making his murders look like suicides investigates his own colleagues when his ex-girlfriend winds up dead.

631012.title: El Último Día (Doblado)
631012.description: Una tormenta apocalíptica amenaza con arrasar todo un país. Se levanta un estado de emergencia mientras estalla el caos.

631544.title: Monsters of Man
631544.description: An illegal U.S. military op goes awry when killer robots are unleashed on heroin producers in Southeast Asia and end up wiping out an entire village.

634414.title: Rapture
634414.description: Survivors of an apocalypse seek refuge while grappling with a poisoned food and water supply, killer lighting, and robed figures vaporizing all life.

637552.title: Out of the Furnace
637552.description: When his ex-Marine little brother disappears after joining a notorious crime syndicate, a Rust Belt steel worker gets armed and goes after him.

638360.title: El Bronco
638360.description: Cuando el taxista Ulises se enamora de la rica Gabriela, hija de un poderoso hombre, se convierte en boxeador profesional para casarse con ella.

639274.title: La Ley Del Monte
639274.description: Una pareja de niños juran amarse toda la vida y graban sus nombres en la penca de un maguey, pero los padres de ella están en contra de su relación.

641661.title: ¡El Que No corre... Vuela!
641661.description: Toda clase de abusos y atropellos sufre la India María en la gran ciudad, sin embargo, ella convierte todo problema en risas y alegría.

642254.title: The Girl with All the Gifts
642254.description: In a bleak future, mankind has succumbed to a fungus that turns everyone into flesh-eating monsters, until an immune child is discovered.

642930.title: Love Sex & Kung Fu
642930.description: After the little sister of a former soldier is kidnapped, she turns into a killing machine, unleashing her fury on anyone who gets in her way.

643079.title: For a Few Dollars More
643079.description: In this classic, truly great spaghetti western, a keen, quick-witted bounty hunter and his fierce rival follow the bloody trail of a murderous outlaw.

644877.title: Rio Lobo
644877.description: Howard Hawks directs John Wayne in a Western about three ex-Civil War soldiers rallying the frontier to rebel against a corrupt and nasty sheriff.

644879.title: Big Jake
644879.description: John Wayne and Maureen O’Hara reunite in this Western about a no-nonsense rancher who hunts down the outlaw gang that abducted his grandson.

647082.title: Doomsday
647082.description: Nearly 30 years after a deadly epidemic swept through Scotland, a commander and her crew search for an antidote when the virus emerges in London.

649977.title: Master Z: Ip Man Legacy (English Dub)
649977.description: Dave Bautista and Michelle Yeoh throw fists in this story of a defeated criminal who gets drawn closer into a life of crime when he becomes a waiter.

652105.title: Lone Rider (Español)
652105.description: Al regresar a su pueblo, un soldado descubre que el corrupto latifundista, mandamás del lugar, quiere adueñarse a las malas del negocio de su familia.

660658.title: Dead Men
660658.description: A young man and his estranged brother embark on a journey to avenge their father’s death, protect the Apache tribe, and reclaim their stolen land.

662071.title: Malibu Shark Attack
662071.description: A tsunami floods Malibu and unleashes a hunting pack of sharks, trapping a group of lifeguards and a team of construction workers in high water.

663440.title: Dead Man Down
663440.description: A hitman for a New York crime lord is seduced and blackmailed by a victim seeking retribution who leads him on a violent and cathartic revenge spree.

664742.title: Speed
664742.description: A city bus with a bomb aboard is set to explode if it falls under 50 mph. An L.A. officer must help one of the passengers steer the bus to safety.

665877.title: Season of the Witch
665877.description: Two 14th-century Crusaders are tasked with routing a suspected witch to a distant monastery to let monks determine if she caused the Black Plague.

665895.title: Corrective Measures
665895.description: As tensions rise among supervillain inmates and corrupt staff, the march toward anarchy begins in the world’s most dangerous maximum-security prison.

668092.title: Tekken 2: Kazuya's Revenge
668092.description: Suffering from amnesia, a young man trying to uncover his identity is abducted by an underground crime ring and turned into a ruthless assassin.

670407.title: The Fifth Element
670407.description: Director Luc Besson's extravagantly-styled, outrageous sci-fi tale of good against evil set in an unbelievable twenty-third century world.

672284.title: Pixels
672284.description: An unlikely group of former '80s video game champions step up to save the world from an alien invasion in this visually spectacular action-adventure.

675529.title: 4 Maras
675529.description: Cinco integrantes de una de las tantas Maras, deciden abandonar la ciudad por la persecución en su contra, pero su líder es arrestado.

676698.title: Mayhem
676698.description: The pent-up rage in an office is unleashed with the spread of a mysterious airborne virus that pits the last two uninfected against their coworkers.

678881.title: Paul Blart: Mall Cop
678881.description: When a shopping mall is taken over by a gang of organized crooks, it's up to a mild-mannered security guard to save the day.

680196.title: Dangerous
680196.description: A reformed sociopath travels to a remote island to uncover the truth behind his brother’s mysterious death, but he's met by a band of mercenaries.

682043.title: A Score to Settle
682043.description: With only a short time to live, Frankie Carver is released from prison, vowing to track down every last member of the gang that betrayed him.

682615.title: The Bourne Ultimatum
682615.description: Jason Bourne flees a new generation of skilled CIA operatives in a non-stop race around the globe while seeking the truth behind his mysterious past.

682628.title: The Bourne Legacy
682628.description: Agent Aaron Cross uses his genetically enhanced skills to evade the CIA after Jason Bourne's actions lead to the termination of his black ops program.

683734.title: Predadores (Doblado)
683734.description: Después de heredar una casa en un remoto pueblo húngaro, un joven se ve envuelto en un conflicto brutal con el magnate local al que desafía.

685920.title: Brawl in Cell Block 99
685920.description: After he's fired from his mechanic gig, a hot-tempered ex-boxer enters the drug-running game which lands him in the battleground of a brutal prison.

688268.title: The Book of Eli
688268.description: Driven by commitment and guided by a belief in something greater than himself, a warrior not by choice but necessity, does what he must to survive.

689543.title: Chain Reaction
689543.description: When his mentor develops a revolutionary clean fuel source, a machinist in an alternative energy lab is ensnared in a web of espionage and murder.

689752.title: Drunken Master
689752.description: After a series of incidents, a mischievous yet righteous young man is sent into a brutal training program run by a master of drunken martial arts.

692126.title: True to the Game 2
692126.description: Based on a NY Times Best Seller, this film picks up a year after the first film and follows the lives of the characters affected by Quadir’s murder.

694227.title: The Rundown
694227.description: A wild action-adventure about a bounty hunter named Beck, who's searching for a rebellious mobster's son and a priceless treasure in the Amazon.

694757.title: Dutch
694757.description: An ambitious heroin dealer has his sights set on becoming the East Coast’s most feared drug lord while battling a high-profile court case.

696007.title: Impact
696007.description: During a 10,000-year meteor shower, a rogue asteroid smashes into the moon and causes disastrous electromagnetic anomalies of weightlessness on Earth.

698965.title: The Jackal
698965.description: An engaging suspense thriller about a ruthless assassin hired to eliminate a powerful, high-ranking official in the U.S. government.

699306.title: Salvaje (Doblado)
699306.description: Después de que su camión se avería, cuatro mujeres se encuentran varadas en una gasolinera y se dan cuenta de que es una trampa mortal.

701400.title: Detective Knight: Rogue
701400.description: While chasing bandits from Los Angeles to New York, detective James Knight crashes into his dark past, imperiling his case—and his life.

701770.title: Danger Close
701770.description: Major Harry Smith leads 108 novice soldiers into an impossible battle in Vietnam that challenges their courage to triumph against overwhelming odds.

702534.title: El Cuatrero
702534.description: Con engaños, Álvaro y Mariana roban una camioneta y un caballo al ranchero Lázaro, quien los busca para recuperar sus pertenencias.

702542.title: Emboscada
702542.description: Dos hombres sospechan de un presidente y le tienden una trampa para desenmascararlo ante el pueblo sin sospechar que descubrirán otras verdades.

702666.title: El Pequeño Soldado (Doblado)
702666.description: Esta película está basada en la historia real de Seryozha Aleshkov, un niño de seis años, el héroe más joven de Rusia en la Segunda Guerra Mundial.

702693.title: El Señor De Las Calles (Doblado)
702693.description: Cuando un entrenador se niega a hacer que su luchador tire una cerilla, un notorio gángster cobra la deuda matando a su luchador y secuestrando a su hija.

703989.title: Ne Zha (English Dub)
703989.description: A young boy destined to destroy the world must choose between good and evil to break the shackles of fate and emerge as the hero he’s desperate to be.

705428.title: Yenni Thuniga
705428.description: After his fiancé is accidentally killed in a jewel heist gone wrong, a man seeks revenge on the gang responsible.

705944.title: Babylon A.D.
705944.description: A ruthless mercenary is hired to smuggle a woman from the post-apocalyptic confines of Eastern Europe to the glittering megalopolis of New York City.

707022.title: Operation Seawolf
707022.description: In the last days of the war, Germany, desperate for any last grasp to defeat the Allied powers, looks to their last remaining weapons and soldiers.

707024.title: A Writer's Odyssey (Dubbed)
707024.description: Years after his child is abducted, a man is hired to kill the author of a fantasy novel, but the world of the novel seems to intersect with reality.

707513.title: Big Stan
707513.description: Panicked he’ll be defenseless in prison, a gutless con man sentenced to hard time for fraud gets 11th hour training from a martial arts master.

708103.title: Wire Room
708103.description: During surveillance, a federal agent witnesses a hit squad murder a surveillance target and soon finds himself in their crosshairs.

708254.title: Samson
708254.description: A child born with supernatural strength in 1200 BC grows up to lead his oppressed tribe with great valor against the mighty empire of his day.

710969.title: Black and Blue
710969.description: After capturing crooked cops killing drug dealers on her body cam, a rookie must evade the narcotics officers after her incriminating evidence.

711946.title: A-X-L
711946.description: A top-secret killer robotic dog developed for the U.S. military develops a special friendship with Miles and will go to any lengths to protect him.

716387.title: Keeping Up with the Joneses
716387.description: Go deep undercover in this comedy about a suburban couple who discovers their neighbors are covert spies embroiled in an international conspiracy.

722519.title: Street (Español)
722519.description: Un luchador que sueña con convertirse en profesional tiene un cambio de destino cuando un gángster ruso lo lleva al mundo del boxeo a puño limpio.

724345.title: Identity Thief
724345.description: A hilarious blockbuster hit about an accounts representative who has one week to clear his name after a con artist steals his identity.

724349.title: The Scorpion King
724349.description: The spectacular Mummy series explodes into a new realm of non-stop action following the epic story of the most feared warrior of the ancient world.

724867.title: The Colony
724867.description: Forced underground by the next ice age, a struggling outpost of survivors fights to preserve humanity against a threat even more savage than nature.

725835.title: El Niño Sicario
725835.description: Pedro es abandonado por sus padres en una estación de autobuses de Sinaloa y al cumplir los 15 años se convierte en un sicario sin corazón.

100000001.title: Kubo and the Two Strings
100000001.description: After accidentally summoning an evil spirit, Kubo must recover his fallen samurai father’s mystical weaponry and discover his own magical powers.

100000104.title: Gun
100000104.description: A new parolee reunites with his former criminal comrade and ignites a full-scale war with Detroit police to defend their business of gun-running.

100000170.title: Maze Runner: The Death Cure
100000170.description: In this epic conclusion, Thomas leads the Gladers on their final mission to break into the legendary Last City—the deadliest maze of all.

100000214.title: Last Action Hero
100000214.description: Jack Slater, a larger-than-life movie hero, helps a young man save his world from an assassin hell-bent on taking it over for himself.

100000216.title: Oldboy
100000216.description: An advertising executive finds himself kidnapped and held hostage for 20 years in solitary confinement without any indication of his captor's motive.

100000556.title: No Escape
100000556.description: A soldier convicted for murdering his commanding officer is dumped and left to die on a prison island inhabited by two camps of convicts.

100000708.title: Equal Standard
100000708.description: After a detective is shot by one of his own NYPD brothers, communities march for justice, and gangs put their differences aside for a united fight.

100000721.title: MacGruber
100000721.description: The former special forces operative and his sidekick set out on a mission to recover a stolen nuclear warhead from his sworn enemy, VonCunth.

100000776.title: El Diablo De Culiacán
100000776.description: El Diablo se ha ganado la confianza de un renombrado narcotraficante, pero comete un error imperdonable que lo envía de vuelta al infierno.

100000864.title: Double Threat
100000864.description: An innocent man on a trip to scatter his brother’s ashes becomes entangled with a woman on the run from the mob after a convenience store shoot-out.

100000946.title: Queen of Kings
100000946.description: Tired of the way she is being treated by the drug lords, dancer Alicia decides to rally her girls to take over the Detroit drug game.

100001153.title: The Samaritan
100001153.description: After being released from prison, a grifter meets a beautiful woman and longs for a fresh start, but first, he has to pull off one last con.

100001240.title: One Shot (Español)
100001240.description: Un francotirador que lucha contra un ejército alienígena debe elegir entre su propia vida y la vida de uno de los mismos seres que quiere matar.

100001316.title: Shark Waters
100001316.description: Miles away from shore, a fishing boat is attacked by great white sharks. Those aboard must fight for their lives to avoid being eaten alive.

100001401.title: No Way Out
100001401.description: Forced to take on a double murder case after the suspect threatens his family, attorney Brian Nelson begins to unravel the facts and learns the case isn’t what it seems.

100001593.title: Shaft
100001593.description: After his friend’s untimely death, cyber security expert John Shaft Jr. teams up with his estranged father to search the city’s criminal underbelly.

100001594.title: Rampage
100001594.description: When a group of animals becomes vicious after a genetic experiment goes awry, a primatologist must find an antidote to avert a global catastrophe.

100001596.title: Mortal Kombat
100001596.description: An MMA fighter with a mysterious dragon birthmark learns that he’s been chosen to fight for Earthrealm in the final battle against the evil Outworld.

100001602.title: Godzilla
100001602.description: A mysterious creature causes a meltdown at a nuclear power plant. Years later, the monster goes on a rampage that can only be stopped by Godzilla.

100001687.title: Tiburón Terrestre (Doblado)
100001687.description: Un grupo científico que intenta modificar genéticamente un tiburón crea una máquina de matar destructiva que ni siquiera ellos pueden controlar.

100001712.title: Detective Knight: Redemption
100001712.description: In the trilogy’s second film, Detective James Knight deals with mercy and justice on his terms when The Christmas Bomber terrorizes the city.

100001718.title: Unlocked
100001718.description: After her mentor asks her to get on a case, a CIA agent works with a former soldier to stop an impending biological attack on London.

100001946.title: El Cholo
100001946.description: Un humilde vendedor de tacos apodado El Sheik, decide unirse a una pandilla para rescatar a Jade que ha sido secuestrada por un conocido padrote.

100001948.title: El Corrido De Silviano Bernal
100001948.description: Para vengar a los que han sido estafados en un casino, Silviano usa sus habilidades para jugar a las cartas para derribar a los dueños, los Márquez.

100002070.title: Bad Cat
100002070.description: A profane house cat must deal with the arrival of his illegitimate son, an accidental killing, his owner's eviction and more within the course of a day of debauchery and mayhem.

100002108.title: The Killer
100002108.description: A retired hitman finds himself on a rescue mission when the 17-year-old girl he's agreed to look after gets in trouble with shady people.

100002112.title: Kill Bill: Vol. 1
100002112.description: After waking up from a four-year coma, a former assassin seeks revenge on the team of killers that betrayed her—and that she was once a part of.

100002159.title: Kill Bill: Vol. 2
100002159.description: The Bride continues her quest for revenge, fighting her way through a host of assassins in pursuit of a final showdown with the man who betrayed her.

100002665.title: The Ambush
100002665.description: When three Emirati soldiers are ambushed by militants in hostile territory, their commander leads a daring mission to rescue them.

100002859.title: 2025 Armageddon
100002859.description: A militant alien race creates real-life versions of giant creatures and geological disasters from Asylum Films titles and uses them to conquer Earth.

0300010104.title: LA's Finest
0300010104.description: A former DEA agent with a complicated past gets partnered with a working mom when she takes a new job as an LAPD detective in this Bad Boys spinoff.

0300008407.title: Nada Es Eterno (Doblado)
0300008407.description: Fue vendida a una poderosa familia, logra escapar, otra familia la acoge por su habilidad para los negocios y el amor llega a su vida inesperadamente.

0300010409.title: Taken
0300010409.description: While dealing with a personal tragedy that shakes his world, CIA agent Bryan Mills fights to overcome the incident and exact revenge.

04718.title: LEGO Ninjago Masters of Spinjitzu
04718.description: Peace has returned to Ninjago, but the four ninja warriors swear to protect and learn to master their Golden Weapons awaiting Lord Garmadon's return.

0300008835.title: Sanctuary
0300008835.description: As gene therapy, transplants and cloning offer hope for humanity, a dark side of evolution produces monsters a select few are brave enough to take on.

0300000087.title: Deputy
0300000087.description: When an elected sheriff dies, an arcane rule in the county charter, forged back in the Wild West, suddenly thrusts the most unlikely man into the job.

04893.title: McGraw Avenue
04893.description: In a notorious Detroit neighborhood, two men with different goals navigate the streets and deal with complex characters, to both survive and dominate.

0300010244.title: Miami Vice
0300010244.description: From executive producer Michael Mann comes the explosive, groundbreaking detective show that redefined the word "cool” in the mid-1980s.

0300008354.title: Airwolf
0300008354.description: A crack test pilot from an elite government intel group flies a supersonic aerial weapon on top secret missions that bypass congressional approval.

0300006557.title: No Easy Days
0300006557.description: After the U.S. President’s daughter is kidnapped, he'll have to enlist a rebellious Navy SEAL—and face his own shortcomings—to get her back.

0300010071.title: Babylon 5
0300010071.description: 2258 CE. The lone space station Babylon 5 stands as the last and best hope for peace between a hundred worlds, alien and human alike.

03854.title: One-Punch Man
03854.description: A hero becomes so strong from training that he can take out his worst foes with one punch, but strength has lost him his hair and fighting passion.

0300009559.title: Farscape
0300009559.description: Thrown into a distant part of the universe, an Earth astronaut finds himself part of a fugitive alien starship crew.

0300010081.title: Nikita
0300010081.description: Betrayed by the secret government agency that made her an assassin, the charming and deadly Nikita makes it her mission to undermine the organization.

01622.title: Naruto (Subtitled)
01622.description: 12 years ago, the Nine-Tailed Fox claimed many lives before its spirit was contained with a baby boy who has now grown to become a ninja-in-training.

0300010102.title: La Femme Nikita
0300010102.description: Condemned to death for a vicious crime she didn't commit, Nikita reluctantly chooses to live as an assassin for a secret government agency.

0300010083.title: The Tomorrow People
0300010083.description: A group of genetically advanced teens with paranormal abilities flee the agents of a paramilitary group on a mission to eradicate them.
